➜Farmers tending flowers at an agriculture base in E China's Shandong
http://www.sohu.com/a/420805595_162758	25834
<p><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20200925/95f107a14fd94ac694bfd6f8df635bcb.jpeg" /></p>
<p>Photo taken on Sept 23, 2020 shows that employees of an industrial poverty alleviation project were tending flowers at Shuangfuhuashi Agricultural Production Base in Liuhu Town, Dongying City, east China's Shandong Province. Dongying has actively implemented industrial poverty alleviation, and has adopted the method of "one village, one product, one household, one policy" by establishing industrial poverty alleviation bases, developing rural e-commerce, rural tourism, etc. (Liu Zhifeng/Guangming Picture)</p>
<p><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20200925/6f6070eabf7547b480d1773814ae32ca.jpeg" /></p>
